      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-google-ranks-images"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Image ranking uses a different algorithm than web search. The key ranking factors include:</p></div></div>
