      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="user-generated-product-images"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Customer photos and review images add authenticity and visual variety. Google indexes these images the same as your professional shots. They often rank for long-tail queries because they show products in real-world settings.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
