    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="running-an-image-seo-audit"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A complete image SEO audit checks 6 areas. Run this audit quarterly or after any major site redesign.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="tracking-image-search-traffic-in-google-search-con">
      <span class="faq-q-text">Tracking Image Search Traffic in Google Search Console</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="tracking-image-search-traffic-in-google-search-con"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p><a href="/blog/google-search-console-guide/">Google Search Console</a> separates image search data from web search data. This is the only free tool that shows exactly how your images perform in Google Images.</p></div></div>
